<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Account Verification - Action Required</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 3px solid #1e40af;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .logo {
            max-width: 120px;
            height: auto;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .status-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #dc2626;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }
        .details {
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #1e40af;
        }
        .detail-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            padding: 8px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }
        .detail-row:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        .label {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #374151;
        }
        .value {
            color: #1f2937;
        }
        .rejection-reason {
            background-color: #fef2f2;
            border-left: 4px solid #dc2626;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            color: #6b7280;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <img src="https://malinta-connect.vercel.app/images/malinta_logo.jpg" alt="Malinta Connect Logo" class="logo">
            <h1 style="color: #1e40af; margin: 0; font-size: 24px;">Account Verification Update</h1>
            <div class="status-badge">NOT APPROVED</div>
        </div>

        <p>Dear <strong><%= residentName %></strong>,</p>

        <p>Thank you for registering with Malinta Connect. Unfortunately, we were unable to verify your account at this time. Please review the information below.</p>

        <% if (notes && notes.trim() !== '') { %>
        <div class="rejection-reason">
            <strong>Reason:</strong><br>
            <%= notes %>
        </div>
        <% } else { %>
        <div class="rejection-reason">
            <strong>Reason:</strong><br>
            Your verification documents could not be approved. Please ensure all information and documents submitted are accurate and meet our requirements.
        </div>
        <% } %>

        <div class="details">
            <h3 style="margin-top: 0; color: #1e40af;">Account Details</h3>
            
            <div class="detail-row">
                <span class="label">Name:</span>
                <span class="value"><%= residentName %></span>
            </div>
            
            <div class="detail-row">
                <span class="label">Email:</span>
                <span class="value"><%= email %></span>
            </div>
            
            <div class="detail-row">
                <span class="label">Review Date:</span>
                <span class="value"><%= verificationDate %></span>
            </div>
            
            <div class="detail-row">
                <span class="label">Status:</span>
                <span class="value"><strong style="color: #dc2626;">Not Approved</strong></span>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div style="background-color: #eff6ff; border-left: 4px solid #3b82f6; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 4px;">
            <strong>What you can do next:</strong><br>
            • Review the reason provided above<br>
            • Ensure your ID photo is clear and valid<br>
            • Make sure your selfie photo matches your ID<br>
            • Verify that all personal information is accurate<br>
            • Contact our office if you need clarification
        </div>

        <p><strong>Common Verification Issues:</strong></p>
        <ul style="color: #6b7280;">
            <li>ID photo is blurry or unreadable</li>
            <li>Selfie photo does not match ID photo</li>
            <li>Expired or invalid identification document</li>
            <li>Incomplete or incorrect personal information</li>
            <li>Documents do not prove residency in Barangay Malinta</li>
        </ul>

        <p>You may need to register again with corrected information and valid documents. If you believe this decision was made in error or need assistance, please contact our office.</p>

        <p><strong>Contact Information:</strong></p>

        <ul style="color: #6b7280;">
            <li><strong>Phone:</strong> +63 912 345 6789</li>
            <li><strong>Email:</strong> barangaymalintalosbanos@gmail.com</li>
            <li><strong>Office Hours:</strong> Monday - Friday, 8:00 AM - 5:00 PM</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>We appreciate your understanding. If you have any questions, please don't hesitate to contact us.</p>
            <p>This is an automated message. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>